    "question_id" : 3109950,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>I agree with the answers already given.</p>\n\n<p>Annotations are part of the <strong>code</strong> while javadoc is part of the <strong>documentation</strong> (hence the name). </p>\n\n<p>So for me it seams reasonable to keep the code parts together.</p>\n"
