    "question_id" : 3109950,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Aside from the coding standard, it seems that javadoc tool doesn't process the javadoc comments if they are placed after the annotations. Works fine otherwise.</p>\n"
