  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3109950/should-i-put-javadoc-before-or-after-annotation",
  "title" : "Should I put Javadoc before or after annotation?",
  "body" : "<p>I can put the Javadoc comment block before or after the annotation. What is the correct way?</p>\n<pre><code>/**\n * This is a javadoc comment before the annotation\n */\n@Component\npublic class MyClass {\n\n    @Autowired\n    /**\n     * This is a javadoc comment after the annotation\n     */\n    private MyOtherClass other;\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
